query:
SELECT 
  p.id,
  p.countryId,
  p.serviceId,
  p.apiId,
  a.name as api_name,
  p.smshubPrice,
  p.ourPrice,
  p.createdAt,
  p.lastSync
FROM prices p
LEFT JOIN sms_apis a ON p.apiId = a.id
WHERE countryId = 1 AND serviceId = 1
ORDER BY p.id;
